# Architecture

Plugin registry on server and client. Game logic → feature plugins; entities + pure functions → focused modules. **Do not** grow monolithic `Game.js` or stub files under `server/systems/`.

## Where to add features

| Task | Where |
|------|--------|
| Socket event | `server/plugins/<feature>/` + `shared/kernel/events.js` |
| Cross-feature side effect (kill → loot) | `registerBus` + `shared/plugins/domainEvents.js` |
| Pure logic (combat, loot, pathfinding) | `shared/plugins/<domain>/` |
| Entity / manager | `server/entities/` |
| Client panel / input | `public/js/plugins/<feature>/` or `plugins/core/` + `InputRouter` |
| Draw pass | `public/js/render/layers/` + `createDefaultLayers.js` |
| Audio / particles | `public/js/audio/`, `shared/plugins/render/particles.js` |
| Modal UI | `public/js/ui/` wired from `plugins/core/index.js` |

Contracts: `shared/plugins/types.js` (`ServerPlugin`, `ClientPlugin`). Register in `server/app/loadPlugins.js` / `public/js/app/loadClientPlugins.js`.

## Key paths

- Bootstrap: `server/app/createServer.js`, `public/js/app/bootstrap.js`
- World sync: `server/app/WorldStateSync.js`, `shared/plugins/world/` (delta, chunks, interest)
- Persistence: `server/persistence/GameDatabase.js` (SQLite)
- Anti-cheat: `shared/plugins/core/anticheat.js`
- Config / debug: `server/config.js`, `server/debug/eventLog.js` (`DEBUG_EVENTS=1`)

## Rules

1. Server authoritative — client sends intent only
2. Plugins use event bus for side effects — no combat → loot direct imports
3. Import canonical paths — `server/entities/`, not deprecated `server/players/` stubs
4. Tests mirror source — see `tests/README.md` for critical gameplay tests
